Below are the steps to run my database project in sql 

1. open mysql wrokbernch 
2. open the file named schema 
3. now create the database using the querry present in schema file
4. now create the tables which all the querries are in the schema file one by one 
5. now enter all the data which are present in the Data_seeding file and run all the querry one by one 
6. Then open the Indexing_strategy.sql which has all the indexing querries also run this 
now you can perform all the crud operation on the tables. 
